import React from "react";
import FloatingLabel from "react-bootstrap/FloatingLabel";
import Form from "react-bootstrap/Form";

export default function RegistrationForm() {
  return (
    <>
    <form>
      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="Nome do veículo"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Nome do veículo" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel controlId="floatingInput" label="Fabricante">
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Fabricante" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="Modelo"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Modelo" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="Ano"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="number" placeholder="Ano" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="Câmbio"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Câmbio" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="Potência"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Potência" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="Torque"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Torque" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="KM"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="KM" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="Cor"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Cor" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="Cabine"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Cabine" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="Relação diferencial"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Relação diferencial" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="Suspensão"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Suspensão" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="Entre eixos"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Entre eixos" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="Capacidade de combustível"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Capacidade de combustível" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="Opcionais"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="textarea" placeholder="Opcionais" />
      </FloatingLabel>

      <FloatingLabel
        controlId="floatingInput"
        label="informações adicionais"
        className="mb-3"
      >
        <Form.Control type="textarea" placeholder="informações adicionais" />
      </FloatingLabel>
    </form>
    </>
  );
}
